reviewText:
it's weather woman to the rescue....this is your run of the mill sexploitation flick.

You know, it's not gonna win a pulitzer prize. And she's certainly not gonna win an Oscar for this performance. But she's hot and what you see is what you get...We all have different preferences, so if Cute Asian girls in short skirts offend you...then you might wanna purchase 'Sleepless in Seattle' instead.
